<div style="margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #666666; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 26px; margin-bottom: 5px; margin-top: 35px; color: #1c3f94;">Dear {{lead.First Name:default=Friend}},</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px; color: #1c3f94;">Join the most popular and quickest-selling community solar program in Massachusetts history!</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">The program has reached 1 Megawatt in sales with more than 140 homeowners signing up to go solar. Many thanks to the homeowners leading the way! We are two-thirds of the way to Mass Energy's goal of 200 sales.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">For the month of July, we are doubling the referral bonus to $200. This means that if you sign a contract for solar before August 31st and you refer a friend in July who also signs a contract by August 31st, you will receive a check for $200.</p>
<p style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-top: 15px;">Click on the REFER A FRIEND button on <a style="color: #61af3f; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;" href="http://www.masssolarconnect.org">www.masssolarconnect.org.</a></p>
<div style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 40px;">
